    "Ensure you have available iCloud storage space. Go to Settings \u2192 [Your Name] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 Manage Storage.": {
      "comment": "Text for checking iCloud storage space.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc0ac\uc6a9 \uac00\ub2a5\ud55c iCloud \uc800\uc7a5 \uacf5\uac04\uc774 \ucda9\ubd84\ud55c\uc9c0 \ud655\uc778\ud558\uc138\uc694. \uc124\uc815 \u2192 [\ub0b4 \uc774\ub984] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 \uc800\uc7a5 \uacf5\uac04 \uad00\ub9ac\ub85c \uc774\ub3d9\ud558\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u786e\u4fdd\u4f60\u6709\u8db3\u591f\u7684 iCloud \u5b58\u50a8\u7a7a\u95f4\u3002\u524d\u5f80 \u8bbe\u7f6e \u2192 [\u4f60\u7684\u540d\u5b57] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 \u7ba1\u7406\u5b58\u50a8\u7a7a\u95f4\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Assurez-vous de disposer d'un espace de stockage iCloud disponible. Acc\u00e9dez \u00e0 Param\u00e8tres \u2192 [Votre nom] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 G\u00e9rer le stockage."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Entries by Year": {
      "comment": "A section header that indicates the content of a view displaying entries organized by the year they were taken.",
