    "Go to Settings \u2192 [Your Name] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 Apps Using iCloud \u2192 Joodle and turn ON the toggle. This is required for sync to work.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc124\uc815 \u2192 [\ub0b4 \uc774\ub984] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 iCloud \uc0ac\uc6a9\ud558\ub294 \uc571 \u2192 Joodle\ub85c \uc774\ub3d9\ud574 \ud1a0\uae00\uc744 \ucf1c\uc138\uc694. \ub3d9\uae30\ud654\uac00 \uc791\ub3d9\ud558\ub824\uba74 \uc774 \uc124\uc815\uc774 \ud544\uc694\ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u524d\u5f80 \u8bbe\u7f6e \u2192 [\u4f60\u7684\u540d\u5b57] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 \u4f7f\u7528 iCloud \u7684 App \u2192 Joodle\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u5f00\u542f\u5f00\u5173\u3002\u540c\u6b65\u529f\u80fd\u9700\u8981\u6b64\u8bbe\u7f6e\u624d\u80fd\u751f\u6548\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Acc\u00e9dez \u00e0 Param\u00e8tres \u2192 [Votre nom] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 Applications utilisant iCloud \u2192 Joodle et activez la bascule. Ceci est n\u00e9cessaire pour que la synchronisation fonctionne."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Go to Settings \u2192 [Your Name] and ensure you're signed in to iCloud.": {
      "comment": "Description of a troubleshooting step where the user should ensure they are signed into their iCloud account.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc124\uc815 \u2192 [\ub0b4 \uc774\ub984]\uc73c\ub85c \uc774\ub3d9\ud574 iCloud\uc5d0 \ub85c\uadf8\uc778\ub418\uc5b4 \uc788\ub294\uc9c0 \ud655\uc778\ud558\uc138\uc694."
