    "Haptic feedback also depends on your device's vibration setting in Settings > Accessibility > Touch > Vibration.": {
      "comment": "A footer message in the Interactions settings view, explaining that haptic feedback is device-specific.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
