          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iCloud indisponible"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "iCloud was disabled in Settings. Please restart the app.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc124\uc815\uc5d0\uc11c iCloud\uac00 \ube44\ud65c\uc131\ud654\ub418\uc5c8\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4. \uc571\uc744 \ub2e4\uc2dc \uc2dc\uc791\ud574 \uc8fc\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u8bbe\u7f6e\u4e2d\u5df2\u505c\u7528 iCloud\u3002\u8bf7\u91cd\u542f\u5e94\u7528\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iCloud a \u00e9t\u00e9 d\u00e9sactiv\u00e9 dans les param\u00e8tres. Veuillez red\u00e9marrer l'application."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If today was a plant, draw how many leaves it grew (or lost) today.": {
      "comment": "A prompt that asks the user to draw how many leaves a plant has grown or lost today.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc624\ub298\uc774 \uc2dd\ubb3c\uc774\ub77c\uba74, \uc624\ub298 \uc78e\uc774 \uc5bc\ub9c8\ub098 \uc790\ub790\ub294\uc9c0(\ub610\ub294 \ub5a8\uc5b4\uc84c\ub294\uc9c0) \uadf8\ub824\ubcf4\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u5982\u679c\u4eca\u5929\u662f\u4e00\u682a\u690d\u7269\uff0c\u753b\u51fa\u5b83\u4eca\u5929\u957f\u51fa\uff08\u6216\u6389\u843d\uff09\u4e86\u591a\u5c11\u7247\u53f6\u5b50\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si c\u2019\u00e9tait aujourd\u2019hui une plante, dessinez combien de feuilles elle a pouss\u00e9 (ou perdue) aujourd\u2019hui."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your brain was a weather map, draw the clouds or sun over it now.": {
      "comment": "A doodling prompt that asks the user to draw a weather map with clouds or a sun.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\ub2f9\uc2e0\uc758 \uba38\ub9bf\uc18d\uc774 \ub0a0\uc528 \uc9c0\ub3c4\ub77c\uba74, \uc9c0\uae08 \uadf8 \uc704\uc5d0 \uad6c\ub984\uc774\ub098 \ud574\ub97c \uadf8\ub824\ubcf4\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u7684\u5927\u8111\u662f\u4e00\u5f20\u5929\u6c14\u56fe\uff0c\u753b\u51fa\u73b0\u5728\u4e0a\u9762\u7684\u4e91\u5f69\u6216\u592a\u9633\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si votre cerveau \u00e9tait une carte m\u00e9t\u00e9o, dessinez maintenant les nuages \u200b\u200bou le soleil dessus."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your focus was a flashlight beam, draw what it is pointing at.": {
      "comment": "A doodling prompt that asks the user to draw what a flashlight beam is pointing at.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc9d1\uc911\ub825\uc774 \uc190\uc804\ub4f1 \ube5b\uc774\ub77c\uba74, \uc9c0\uae08 \ubb34\uc5c7\uc744 \ube44\ucd94\uace0 \uc788\ub294\uc9c0 \uadf8\ub824\ubcf4\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u7684\u6ce8\u610f\u529b\u662f\u4e00\u675f\u624b\u7535\u7b52\u5149\uff0c\u753b\u51fa\u5b83\u6b63\u7167\u5411\u4ec0\u4e48\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si votre objectif \u00e9tait le faisceau d\u2019une lampe de poche, dessinez ce vers quoi il pointe."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your stress was a jar of tangled wires, draw how messy the wires are.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc2a4\ud2b8\ub808\uc2a4\uac00 \uc5c9\ud0a8 \uc804\uc120\uc774 \ub2f4\uae34 \ubcd1\uc774\ub77c\uba74, \uc804\uc120\uc774 \uc5bc\ub9c8\ub098 \ubcf5\uc7a1\ud55c\uc9c0 \uadf8\ub824\ubcf4\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u7684\u538b\u529b\u662f\u4e00\u7f50\u7f20\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u7684\u7535\u7ebf\uff0c\u753b\u51fa\u8fd9\u4e9b\u7535\u7ebf\u6709\u591a\u4e71\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Si votre stress \u00e9tait un pot de fils emm\u00eal\u00e9s, dessinez \u00e0 quel point les fils sont en d\u00e9sordre."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Imagine seeing a year of your life in a single glance. Each Joodle carries a special piece of memory. Always private. Always yours.": {
      "comment": "A description of the feature that allows users to see all their past Joodles in one place.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc778\uc0dd\uc758 1\ub144\uc744 \ud55c\ub208\uc5d0 \ubcf8\ub2e4\uace0 \uc0c1\uc0c1\ud574 \ubcf4\uc138\uc694. \uac01 Joodle\uc5d0\ub294 \ud2b9\ubcc4\ud55c \uae30\uc5b5\uc758 \uc870\uac01\uc774 \ub2f4\uaca8 \uc788\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4. \uc5b8\uc81c\ub098 \ube44\uacf5\uac1c. \uc5b8\uc81c\ub098 \ub2f9\uc2e0\uc758 \uac83."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u60f3\u8c61\u4e00\u773c\u7eb5\u89c8\u4f60\u4e00\u6574\u5e74\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\u3002\u6bcf\u4e2a\u6d82\u9e26\u627f\u8f7d\u7740\u4e00\u6bb5\u7279\u522b\u7684\u8bb0\u5fc6\u3002\u59cb\u7ec8\u79c1\u5bc6\u3002\u59cb\u7ec8\u5c5e\u4e8e\u4f60\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Imaginez voir une ann\u00e9e de votre vie d\u2019un seul coup d\u2019\u0153il. Chaque Joodle transporte un morceau de m\u00e9moire sp\u00e9cial. Toujours priv\u00e9. Toujours \u00e0 vous."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Import complete": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uac00\uc838\uc624\uae30 \uc644\ub8cc"
