          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\ud648 \ud654\uba74\uc744 \uae38\uac8c \ub204\ub974\uace0 + \ubc84\ud2bc\uc744 \ud0ed\ud55c \ub4a4 \"Joodle\"\uc744 \uac80\uc0c9\ud574 \uc704\uc82f\uc744 \ucd94\uac00\ud558\uc138\uc694. \uc77c\ubd80 \uc704\uc82f\uc740 \uad6c\uc131\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\uc73c\uba70, \ud3b8\uc9d1 \ubaa8\ub4dc\uc5d0\uc11c \uc704\uc82f\uc744 \ud0ed\ud574 \uc124\uc815\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u957f\u6309\u4e3b\u5c4f\u5e55\uff0c\u70b9\u51fb + \u6309\u94ae\uff0c\u641c\u7d22\"Joodle\"\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u6dfb\u52a0\u5c0f\u7ec4\u4ef6\u3002\u90e8\u5206\u5c0f\u7ec4\u4ef6\u652f\u6301\u914d\u7f6e\uff0c\u5728\u7f16\u8f91\u6a21\u5f0f\u4e0b\u70b9\u51fb\u5c0f\u7ec4\u4ef6\u5373\u53ef\u8fdb\u884c\u8bbe\u7f6e\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Appuyez longuement sur votre \u00e9cran d'accueil, appuyez sur le bouton +, recherchez \u00ab Joodle \u00bb et ajoutez un widget. Certains widgets sont configurables. Appuyez sur le widget en mode \u00e9dition pour le configurer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Long press on your lock screen, tap \"Customize\", then \"ADD WIDGETS\", find \"Joodle\", and tap or drag the widget onto the lock screen.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc7a0\uae08 \ud654\uba74\uc744 \uae38\uac8c \ub204\ub978 \ub4a4 \"\uc0ac\uc6a9\uc790\ud654\"\ub97c \ud0ed\ud558\uace0 \"\uc704\uc82f \ucd94\uac00\"\ub97c \uc120\ud0dd\ud558\uc138\uc694. \"Joodle\"\uc744 \ucc3e\uc544 \ud0ed\ud558\uac70\ub098 \ub04c\uc5b4\uc11c \uc7a0\uae08 \ud654\uba74\uc5d0 \ucd94\uac00\ud558\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u957f\u6309\u9501\u5c4f\u754c\u9762\uff0c\u70b9\u51fb\"\u81ea\u5b9a\"\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u9009\u62e9\"\u6dfb\u52a0\u5c0f\u7ec4\u4ef6\"\uff0c\u627e\u5230\"Joodle\"\uff0c\u70b9\u51fb\u6216\u62d6\u62fd\u5c0f\u7ec4\u4ef6\u5230\u9501\u5c4f\u4e0a\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Appuyez longuement sur votre \u00e9cran de verrouillage, appuyez sur \u00ab Personnaliser \u00bb, puis \u00ab AJOUTER DES WIDGETS \u00bb, recherchez \u00ab Joodle \u00bb et appuyez ou faites glisser le widget sur l'\u00e9cran de verrouillage."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Long press your doodle and tap the option to \"Move to Another Date\"": {
      "comment": "Text displayed in a tutorial tooltip when a user long-presses a drawing to open a context menu with an option to \"Move to Another Date\".",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\ub099\uc11c\ub97c \uae38\uac8c \ub204\ub978 \ud6c4 \"\ub2e4\ub978 \ub0a0\uc9dc\ub85c \uc774\ub3d9\" \uc635\uc158\uc744 \ud0ed\ud558\uc138\uc694"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u957f\u6309\u4f60\u7684\u6d82\u9e26\u7136\u540e\u9009\u62e9\"\u79fb\u52a8\u5230\u5176\u4ed6\u65e5\u671f\""
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Appuyez longuement sur votre doodle et appuyez sur l'option \"D\u00e9placer vers une autre date\"."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Long press, tap the + button, search for \"Joodle\", and add a widget. Some widgets are configurable. Tap the widget while in edit mode to configure.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uae38\uac8c \ub204\ub978 \ud6c4 + \ubc84\ud2bc\uc744 \ud0ed\ud558\uace0 \"Joodle\"\uc744 \uac80\uc0c9\ud574 \uc704\uc82f\uc744 \ucd94\uac00\ud558\uc138\uc694. \uc77c\ubd80 \uc704\uc82f\uc740 \ud3b8\uc9d1 \ubaa8\ub4dc\uc5d0\uc11c \ud0ed\ud574 \uad6c\uc131\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u957f\u6309\uff0c\u70b9\u51fb + \u6309\u94ae\uff0c\u641c\u7d22\"Joodle\"\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u6dfb\u52a0\u5c0f\u7ec4\u4ef6\u3002\u90e8\u5206\u5c0f\u7ec4\u4ef6\u652f\u6301\u914d\u7f6e\uff0c\u5728\u7f16\u8f91\u6a21\u5f0f\u4e0b\u70b9\u51fb\u5c0f\u7ec4\u4ef6\u5373\u53ef\u8fdb\u884c\u8bbe\u7f6e\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Appuyez longuement, appuyez sur le bouton +, recherchez \u00ab Joodle \u00bb et ajoutez un widget. Certains widgets sont configurables. Appuyez sur le widget en mode \u00e9dition pour le configurer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Look at your dominant hand. Draw the shape it makes resting on your lap.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc8fc\ub85c \uc4f0\ub294 \uc190\uc744 \ubcf4\uc138\uc694. \ubb34\ub98e \uc704\uc5d0 \uc62c\ub824\ub454 \ubaa8\uc591\uc744 \uadf8\ub824\ubcf4\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u770b\u770b\u4f60\u5e38\u7528\u7684\u90a3\u53ea\u624b\u3002\u753b\u51fa\u5b83\u653e\u5728\u4f60\u817f\u4e0a\u7684\u5f62\u72b6\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Regardez votre main dominante. Dessinez la forme qu'il fait reposer sur vos genoux."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Look up. What is the shape of the cloud or the patch of sky you see?": {
      "comment": "A doodling prompt that encourages the user to draw the shape of a cloud or sky patch they see in the sky.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uace0\uac1c\ub97c \ub4e4\uc5b4\ubcf4\uc138\uc694. \ubcf4\uc774\ub294 \uad6c\ub984\uc774\ub098 \ud558\ub298 \uc870\uac01\uc740 \uc5b4\ub5a4 \ubaa8\uc591\uc778\uac00\uc694?"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u62ac\u5934\u770b\u3002\u4f60\u770b\u5230\u7684\u4e91\u6735\u6216\u8005\u5929\u7a7a\u662f\u4ec0\u4e48\u5f62\u72b6\uff1f"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chercher. Quelle est la forme du nuage ou de la partie du ciel que vous voyez\u00a0?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Made with Joodle": {
      "comment": "A text label displayed as a watermark at the bottom-right corner of the screen, indicating that the app was developed using Joodle.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Made with Joodle"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u7531 Joodle \u5236\u4f5c"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "R\u00e9alis\u00e9 avec Joodle"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Make sure you are on TestFlight. Take a screenshot, then tap \"Share Beta Feedback...\". Write \"I want promo code\" in the feedback section. And most importantly, include your email address in \"Share Your Email\" section so that we can send the code to you!": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "TestFlight \ubc84\uc804\uc744 \uc0ac\uc6a9 \uc911\uc778\uc9c0 \ud655\uc778\ud558\uc138\uc694. \uc2a4\ud06c\ub9b0\uc0f7\uc744 \ucc0d\uc740 \ub4a4 \"Share Beta Feedback...\"\ub97c \ud0ed\ud558\uc138\uc694. \ud53c\ub4dc\ubc31\uc5d0 \"I want promo code\"\ub77c\uace0 \uc791\uc131\ud574 \uc8fc\uc138\uc694. \uadf8\ub9ac\uace0 \uac00\uc7a5 \uc911\uc694\ud558\uac8c \"Share Your Email\" \uc139\uc158\uc5d0 \uc774\uba54\uc77c \uc8fc\uc18c\ub97c \ud3ec\ud568\ud574\uc57c \ucf54\ub4dc\ub97c \ubcf4\ub0b4\ub4dc\ub9b4 \uc218 \uc788\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4!"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u786e\u4fdd\u4f60\u6b63\u5728\u4f7f\u7528 TestFlight \u7248\u672c\u3002\u622a\u53d6\u4e00\u5f20\u622a\u56fe\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u70b9\u51fb\"\u5206\u4eab Beta \u53cd\u9988\u2026\"\u3002\u5728\u53cd\u9988\u90e8\u5206\u5199\u4e0b\"\u6211\u60f3\u8981\u4fc3\u9500\u7801\"\u3002\u6700\u91cd\u8981\u7684\u662f\uff0c\u5728\"\u5206\u4eab\u4f60\u7684\u90ae\u7bb1\"\u90e8\u5206\u586b\u5199\u4f60\u7684\u90ae\u7bb1\u5730\u5740\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u6211\u4eec\u5c06\u5151\u6362\u7801\u53d1\u9001\u7ed9\u4f60\uff01"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Assurez-vous que vous \u00eates sur TestFlight. Prenez une capture d'\u00e9cran, puis appuyez sur \"Partager les commentaires sur la b\u00eata...\". \u00c9crivez \u00ab\u00a0Je veux un code promotionnel\u00a0\u00bb dans la section commentaires. Et surtout, indiquez votre adresse e-mail dans la section \u00ab Partager votre e-mail \u00bb afin que nous puissions vous envoyer le code !"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Make sure you have an active internet connection (Wi-Fi or cellular data). Current status: %@": {
      "comment": "A description of a troubleshooting step related to the internet connection. The text inside the placeholder variable will be replaced with the actual network connection status.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\ud65c\uc131 \uc778\ud130\ub137 \uc5f0\uacb0(Wi-Fi \ub610\ub294 \uc140\ub8f0\ub7ec \ub370\uc774\ud130)\uc774 \uc788\ub294\uc9c0 \ud655\uc778\ud558\uc138\uc694. \ud604\uc7ac \uc0c1\ud0dc: %@"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u786e\u4fdd\u4f60\u6709\u6709\u6548\u7684\u7f51\u7edc\u8fde\u63a5\uff08Wi-Fi \u6216\u8702\u7a9d\u6570\u636e\uff09\u3002\u5f53\u524d\u72b6\u6001\uff1a%@"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Assurez-vous de disposer d'une connexion Internet active (Wi-Fi ou donn\u00e9es cellulaires). Statut actuel\u00a0:\u00a0%@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Manage or Cancel via App Store": {
      "comment": "A button label that directs users to manage or cancel their subscription via the App Store.",
