    "Open Spotlight Search by swiping down on home screen. Search for \"Joodle\". Tap on any quick action.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\ud648 \ud654\uba74\uc5d0\uc11c \uc544\ub798\ub85c \uc4f8\uc5b4 Spotlight \uac80\uc0c9\uc744 \uc5f4\uace0 \"Joodle\"\uc744 \uac80\uc0c9\ud558\uc138\uc694. \uc6d0\ud558\ub294 \ube60\ub978 \ub3d9\uc791\uc744 \ud0ed\ud558\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u5728\u4e3b\u5c4f\u5e55\u5411\u4e0b\u6ed1\u52a8\u6253\u5f00\u805a\u7126\u641c\u7d22\u3002\u641c\u7d22\"Joodle\"\u3002\u70b9\u51fb\u4efb\u610f\u5feb\u6377\u64cd\u4f5c\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ouvrez la recherche Spotlight en faisant glisser votre doigt vers le bas sur l'\u00e9cran d'accueil. Recherchez \"Joodle\". Appuyez sur n\u2019importe quelle action rapide."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open your Joodle and let your fingertips capture the moments that matter. Each stroke adds a memory, building a collection that grows with you.": {
      "comment": "A description of the functionality of the app, emphasizing the creation and sharing of memories.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Joodle\uc744 \uc5f4\uace0 \uc190\ub05d\uc73c\ub85c \uc18c\uc911\ud55c \uc21c\uac04\uc744 \ub2f4\uc544\ubcf4\uc138\uc694. \ud55c \ubc88\uc758 \uc120\ub9c8\ub2e4 \uae30\uc5b5\uc774 \ub354\ud574\uc838, \ub2f9\uc2e0\uacfc \ud568\uaed8 \uc790\ub77c\ub294 \uceec\ub809\uc158\uc774 \ub429\ub2c8\ub2e4."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u6253\u5f00\u4f60\u7684\u6d82\u9e26\u65e5\u8bb0\uff0c\u8ba9\u6307\u5c16\u6355\u6349\u6bcf\u4e00\u4e2a\u91cd\u8981\u65f6\u523b\u3002\u6bcf\u4e00\u7b14\u90fd\u662f\u4e00\u6bb5\u8bb0\u5fc6\uff0c\u6c47\u805a\u6210\u4e0e\u4f60\u5171\u540c\u6210\u957f\u7684\u6536\u85cf\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ouvrez votre Joodle et laissez vos doigts capturer les moments qui comptent. Chaque trait ajoute un souvenir, cr\u00e9ant ainsi une collection qui grandit avec vous."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Opens Joodle to create or edit today's doodle entry": {
      "comment": "Description of the intent that opens the app to create or edit today's doodle entry.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Joodle\uc744 \uc5f4\uc5b4 \uc624\ub298\uc758 \ub099\uc11c \ud56d\ubaa9\uc744 \uc0dd\uc131\ud558\uac70\ub098 \ud3b8\uc9d1\ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
