    "Swipe left to delete, or tap Edit to select multiple alarms.": {
      "comment": "A footer message in the Anniversary Alarms Settings View, instructing the user on how to interact with the list of alarms.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc67c\ucabd\uc73c\ub85c \ubc00\uc5b4 \uc0ad\uc81c\ud558\uac70\ub098, \ud3b8\uc9d1\uc744 \ub20c\ub7ec \uc5ec\ub7ec \uc54c\ub9bc\uc744 \uc120\ud0dd\ud558\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u5411\u5de6\u6ed1\u52a8\u5220\u9664\uff0c\u6216\u70b9\u51fb\u7f16\u8f91\u4ee5\u9009\u62e9\u591a\u4e2a\u95f9\u949f\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Faites glisser votre doigt vers la gauche pour supprimer ou appuyez sur Modifier pour s\u00e9lectionner plusieurs alarmes."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Switch Plan": {
      "comment": "The title of the view.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uc694\uae08\uc81c \ubcc0\uacbd"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u5207\u6362\u65b9\u6848"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Changer de forfait"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Switching between subscription plans is handled by the App Store. Tap a new plan to purchase it, or use \"Manage or Cancel via App Store\" to change or cancel your current subscription.": {
      "comment": "A disclaimer explaining that switching between subscription plans is managed by the App Store, and that users can manage or cancel their subscriptions through the App Store.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\uad6c\ub3c5 \uc694\uae08\uc81c \uc804\ud658\uc740 App Store\uc5d0\uc11c \ucc98\ub9ac\ub429\ub2c8\ub2e4. \uc0c8 \uc694\uae08\uc81c\ub97c \ud0ed\ud574 \uad6c\ub9e4\ud558\uac70\ub098 \"App Store\ub97c \ud1b5\ud574 \uad00\ub9ac \ub610\ub294 \ucde8\uc18c\"\ub97c \uc0ac\uc6a9\ud574 \ud604\uc7ac \uad6c\ub3c5\uc744 \ubcc0\uacbd\ud558\uac70\ub098 \ucde8\uc18c\ud558\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u8ba2\u9605\u65b9\u6848\u5207\u6362\u7531 App Store \u5904\u7406\u3002\u70b9\u51fb\u65b0\u65b9\u6848\u5373\u53ef\u8d2d\u4e70\uff0c\u6216\u4f7f\u7528\"\u901a\u8fc7 App Store \u7ba1\u7406\u6216\u53d6\u6d88\"\u6765\u53d8\u66f4\u6216\u53d6\u6d88\u5f53\u524d\u8ba2\u9605\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le basculement entre les plans d\u2019abonnement est g\u00e9r\u00e9 par l\u2019App Store. Appuyez sur un nouveau forfait pour l'acheter ou utilisez \u00ab G\u00e9rer ou annuler via l'App Store \u00bb pour modifier ou annuler votre abonnement actuel."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Switching to %@ (%@) at next renewal": {
      "comment": "A line that explains that a user's subscription plan is set to change at the next renewal.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Switching to %1$@ (%2$@) at next renewal"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\ub2e4\uc74c \uac31\uc2e0 \uc2dc %1$@ (%2$@)\uc73c\ub85c \uc804\ud658"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u4e0b\u6b21\u7eed\u8d39\u65f6\u5207\u6362\u5230%@\uff08%@\uff09"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Passer \u00e0 %1$@ (%2$@) lors du prochain renouvellement"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Switching to %@ (%@) on %@": {
      "comment": "A label announcing that a user is switching to a new in-app purchase plan, including the name of the plan, its price, and the date it will take effect. The date is formatted to show the month and day.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Switching to %1$@ (%2$@) on %3$@"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%3$@\uc5d0 %1$@ (%2$@)\uc73c\ub85c \uc804\ud658"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u5c06\u4e8e%@\u5207\u6362\u5230%@\uff08%@\uff09"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Passage \u00e0 %1$@ (%2$@) sur %3$@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Swtich to \"Normal\" view mode, then scroll to the top of the grid, continue to scroll and you should see the weekday labels. To change the Start of Week, go to \"Settings\" > \"General\" > \"Customization\" > \"Start of Week\".": {
      "comment": "Description of a tutorial that teaches how to view weekday labels in \"Normal\" view mode.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\uc77c\ubc18\" \ubcf4\uae30 \ubaa8\ub4dc\ub85c \uc804\ud658\ud55c \ub4a4 \uadf8\ub9ac\ub4dc \ub9e8 \uc704\uae4c\uc9c0 \uc2a4\ud06c\ub864\ud558\uace0, \uacc4\uc18d \uc2a4\ud06c\ub864\ud558\uba74 \uc694\uc77c \ub77c\ubca8\uc774 \ubcf4\uc785\ub2c8\ub2e4. \uc8fc \uc2dc\uc791\uc77c\uc744 \ubc14\uafb8\ub824\uba74 \"\uc124\uc815\" > \"\uc77c\ubc18\" > \"\uc0ac\uc6a9\uc790\ud654\" > \"\uc8fc \uc2dc\uc791\uc77c\"\ub85c \uc774\ub3d9\ud558\uc138\uc694."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u5207\u6362\u5230\"\u5e38\u89c4\"\u89c6\u56fe\u6a21\u5f0f\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u6eda\u52a8\u5230\u7f51\u683c\u9876\u90e8\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u5411\u4e0a\u6eda\u52a8\u5373\u53ef\u770b\u5230\u661f\u671f\u6807\u7b7e\u3002\u8981\u66f4\u6539\u6bcf\u5468\u8d77\u59cb\u65e5\uff0c\u8bf7\u524d\u5f80\"\u8bbe\u7f6e\" > \"\u901a\u7528\" > \"\u81ea\u5b9a\u4e49\" > \"\u6bcf\u5468\u8d77\u59cb\u65e5\"\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Passez en mode d'affichage \"Normal\", puis faites d\u00e9filer vers le haut de la grille, continuez \u00e0 faire d\u00e9filer et vous devriez voir les \u00e9tiquettes des jours de la semaine. Pour modifier le d\u00e9but de la semaine, allez dans \u00ab Param\u00e8tres \u00bb > \u00ab G\u00e9n\u00e9ral \u00bb > \u00ab Personnalisation \u00bb > \u00ab D\u00e9but de la semaine \u00bb."
          }
        }
      }
    },
