            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Conseils et tutoriels"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "To enable iCloud sync, Joodle needs to close and restart.\n\nYour data is safe and will sync to iCloud when you reopen the app.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "iCloud \ub3d9\uae30\ud654\ub97c \ud65c\uc131\ud654\ud558\ub824\uba74 Joodle\uc744 \uc885\ub8cc\ud558\uace0 \ub2e4\uc2dc \uc2dc\uc791\ud574\uc57c \ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4.\n\n\ub370\uc774\ud130\ub294 \uc548\uc804\ud558\uba70 \uc571\uc744 \ub2e4\uc2dc \uc5f4\uba74 iCloud\ub85c \ub3d9\uae30\ud654\ub429\ub2c8\ub2e4."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u8981\u542f\u7528  iCloud\u4e91\u670d\u52a1\u540c\u6b65\uff0cJoodle \u9700\u8981\u5173\u95ed\u5e76\u91cd\u542f\u3002\n\n\u4f60\u7684\u6570\u636e\u662f\u5b89\u5168\u7684\uff0c\u91cd\u65b0\u6253\u5f00\u5e94\u7528\u540e\u5c06\u540c\u6b65\u5230 iCloud\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pour activer la synchronisation iCloud, Joodle doit se fermer et red\u00e9marrer.\n\nVos donn\u00e9es sont en s\u00e9curit\u00e9 et seront synchronis\u00e9es avec iCloud lorsque vous rouvrirez l'application."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "To enable sync, you must enable \"Saved to iCloud\" for Joodle in iCloud Settings: Settings \u2192 [Your Name] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 Saved to iCloud \u2192 Joodle.": {
      "comment": "A description explaining how to enable iCloud sync.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\ub3d9\uae30\ud654\ub97c \ud65c\uc131\ud654\ud558\ub824\uba74 iCloud \uc124\uc815\uc5d0\uc11c Joodle\uc758 \"iCloud\uc5d0 \uc800\uc7a5\ub428\"\uc744 \ucf1c\uc57c \ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4: \uc124\uc815 \u2192 [\uc0ac\uc6a9\uc790 \uc774\ub984] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 iCloud\uc5d0 \uc800\uc7a5\ub428 \u2192 Joodle."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u8981\u542f\u7528\u540c\u6b65\uff0c\u4f60\u9700\u8981\u5728 iCloud \u8bbe\u7f6e\u4e2d\u4e3a Joodle \u542f\u7528\"\u4fdd\u5b58\u5230 iCloud\"\uff1a\u8bbe\u7f6e \u2192 [\u4f60\u7684\u540d\u5b57] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 \u4fdd\u5b58\u5230 iCloud \u2192 Joodle\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pour activer la synchronisation, vous devez activer \u00ab\u00a0Enregistr\u00e9 sur iCloud\u00a0\u00bb pour Joodle dans les param\u00e8tres iCloud\u00a0: Param\u00e8tres \u2192 [Votre nom] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 Enregistr\u00e9 sur iCloud \u2192 Joodle."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "To enable sync, you must enable \"Saved to iCloud\" for Joodle in iCloud Settings: Settings \u2192 [Your Name] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 Saved to iCloud \u2192 Joodle. ": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\ub3d9\uae30\ud654\ub97c \ud65c\uc131\ud654\ud558\ub824\uba74 iCloud \uc124\uc815\uc5d0\uc11c Joodle\uc758 \"iCloud\uc5d0 \uc800\uc7a5\ub428\"\uc744 \ucf1c\uc57c \ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4: \uc124\uc815 \u2192 [\uc0ac\uc6a9\uc790 \uc774\ub984] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 iCloud\uc5d0 \uc800\uc7a5\ub428 \u2192 Joodle."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u8981\u542f\u7528\u540c\u6b65\uff0c\u4f60\u9700\u8981\u5728 iCloud \u8bbe\u7f6e\u4e2d\u4e3a Joodle \u542f\u7528\"\u4fdd\u5b58\u5230 iCloud\"\uff1a\u8bbe\u7f6e \u2192 [\u4f60\u7684\u540d\u5b57] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 \u4fdd\u5b58\u5230 iCloud \u2192 Joodle\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pour activer la synchronisation, vous devez activer \u00ab\u00a0Enregistr\u00e9 sur iCloud\u00a0\u00bb pour Joodle dans les param\u00e8tres iCloud\u00a0: Param\u00e8tres \u2192 [Votre nom] \u2192 iCloud \u2192 Enregistr\u00e9 sur iCloud \u2192 Joodle. "
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "To start syncing your Joodles to iCloud, Joodle needs to restart.\n\nYour Joodle has been saved and will sync after restart.": {
      "comment": "An alert message that appears when a user is prompted to restart their device in order to enable iCloud sync.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Joodle\uc744 iCloud\uc640 \ub3d9\uae30\ud654\ud558\ub824\uba74 Joodle\uc744 \ub2e4\uc2dc \uc2dc\uc791\ud574\uc57c \ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4.\n\nJoodle\uc740 \uc774\ubbf8 \uc800\uc7a5\ub418\uc5c8\uc73c\uba70 \uc7ac\uc2dc\uc791 \ud6c4 \ub3d9\uae30\ud654\ub429\ub2c8\ub2e4."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u8981\u5f00\u59cb\u5c06\u4f60\u7684\u6d82\u9e26\u540c\u6b65\u5230 iCloud\uff0cJoodle \u9700\u8981\u91cd\u542f\u3002\n\n\u4f60\u7684\u6d82\u9e26\u5df2\u4fdd\u5b58\uff0c\u91cd\u542f\u540e\u5c06\u5f00\u59cb\u540c\u6b65\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pour commencer \u00e0 synchroniser vos Joodles avec iCloud, Joodle doit red\u00e9marrer.\n\nVotre Joodle a \u00e9t\u00e9 enregistr\u00e9 et sera synchronis\u00e9 apr\u00e8s le red\u00e9marrage."
          }
        }
      }
    },
