          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u542f\u7528\u540e\uff0cJoodle \u4f1a\u81ea\u52a8\u5c06\u4f60\u7684\u65e5\u8bb0\u8bb0\u5f55\u548c\u504f\u597d\u8bbe\u7f6e\u540c\u6b65\u5230 iCloud\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lorsqu'il est activ\u00e9, Joodle synchronise automatiquement vos entr\u00e9es de journal et vos pr\u00e9f\u00e9rences avec iCloud."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When enabled, the app will behave as if it's running in production (App Store release).": {
      "comment": "A footer description for the \"Developer Options\" section in the settings view, explaining that enabling this feature will make the app behave as if it's running in production mode (i.e. on an actual device",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\ud65c\uc131\ud654\ud558\uba74 \uc571\uc774 \ud504\ub85c\ub355\uc158(App Store \ubc30\ud3ec\ubcf8)\uc5d0\uc11c \uc2e4\ud589\ub418\ub294 \uac83\ucc98\ub7fc \ub3d9\uc791\ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u542f\u7528\u540e\uff0c\u5e94\u7528\u5c06\u6a21\u62df\u751f\u4ea7\u73af\u5883\uff08App Store \u53d1\u5e03\u7248\uff09\u8fd0\u884c\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lorsqu'elle est activ\u00e9e, l'application se comportera comme si elle \u00e9tait ex\u00e9cut\u00e9e en production (version App Store)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When enabled, you may occasionally see announcements when opening the app. You can customize which types of announcements you'd like to receive below.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\ud65c\uc131\ud654\ud558\uba74 \uc571\uc744 \uc5f4 \ub54c \uac00\ub054 \uacf5\uc9c0\ub97c \ubcfc \uc218 \uc788\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4. \uc544\ub798\uc5d0\uc11c \ubc1b\uace0 \uc2f6\uc740 \uacf5\uc9c0 \uc720\ud615\uc744 \uc124\uc815\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\u542f\u7528\u540e\uff0c\u6253\u5f00\u5e94\u7528\u65f6\u4f60\u53ef\u80fd\u5076\u5c14\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u516c\u544a\u3002\u4f60\u53ef\u4ee5\u5728\u4e0b\u65b9\u81ea\u5b9a\u4e49\u60f3\u63a5\u6536\u7684\u516c\u544a\u7c7b\u578b\u3002"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lorsqu'il est activ\u00e9, vous pouvez parfois voir des annonces lors de l'ouverture de l'application. Vous pouvez personnaliser les types d'annonces que vous souhaitez recevoir ci-dessous."
          }
        }
      }
    },
